Q38: Write an INNER JOIN query to list employee names and their corresponding
department names.
SQL> SELECT e.emp_name, d.dept_name FROM employee109 e INNER JOIN department109 d ON e.dept_id = d.dept_id;

EMP_NAME					   DEPT_NAME
-------------------------------------------------- --------------------
Shidha						   Computer Science
Sophia Joshy         Finance
Karthik K					   Finance
Joseph Sunny         Finance
Santhosh					   Finance
Sona Mary					   Mechanical
Sujesh						   Civil
Deepa                MCA

