Q39: Use a LEFT JOIN to list all employees and their department names, including those
who do not belong to any department.
SQL> SELECT e.emp_name, d.dept_name FROM employee109 e LEFT JOIN department109 d ON e.dept_id = d.dept_id;

EMP_NAME					   DEPT_NAME
-------------------------------------------------- --------------------
Shidha						   Computer Science
