Q40: Write a RIGHT JOIN to list all departments and their corresponding employees,
including departments with no employees.
SQL> SELECT e.emp_name, d.dept_name FROM employee109 e RIGHT JOIN department109 d ON e.dept_id = d.dept_id;

EMP_NAME					   DEPT_NAME
-------------------------------------------------- --------------------
